Main article: Super Smash Bros.Super Smash Bros. was introduced in 1999 for the Nintendo 64.
Main article: Super Smash Bros. BrawlAlthough a third Super Smash Bros. game had been announced long before E3 2006, Nintendo unveiled its first information in the form of a trailer on May 10, 2006, and the game was named Super Smash Bros. Brawl.
Super Smash Bros. Brawl features a new Adventure Mode titled Super Smash Bros. Brawl: The Subspace Emissary.
